    <item>
      <title>在GNU/Linux中安裝Docker CE（社區版）全記錄</title>
      <link>https://luolvshi.me/hugo2/zh/2017/installing-and-configuring-docker-community-edition-ce-on-gnu-linux/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 Mar 2017 13:24:08 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://luolvshi.me/hugo2/zh/2017/installing-and-configuring-docker-community-edition-ce-on-gnu-linux/</guid>
      
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.docker.com&#34; title=&#34;Docker&#34;&gt;Docker&lt;/a&gt;是一款開源的，提供&lt;code&gt;Operating-system-level virtualization&lt;/code&gt;(操作系統級別的虛擬化的)容器(container)產品，可實現在軟件容器中自動部署應用。目前有&lt;code&gt;Enterprise Edition(EE)&lt;/code&gt;、&lt;code&gt;Community Edition(CE)&lt;/code&gt;、&lt;code&gt;Cloud&lt;/code&gt;三個變種。本文記錄在GNU/Linux中安裝、配置Docker Engine的過程，並通過&lt;a href=&#34;#shell-script&#34;&gt;Shell Script&lt;/a&gt;實現。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>主流GNU/Linux發行版的產品支持週期信息</title>
      <link>https://luolvshi.me/hugo2/zh/2017/product-support-life-cycle-info-for-mainstream-gnu-linux-distributions/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Feb 2017 13:40:36 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://luolvshi.me/hugo2/zh/2017/product-support-life-cycle-info-for-mainstream-gnu-linux-distributions/</guid>
      
        <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.gnu.org&#34; title=&#34;GNU Operating System&#34;&gt;GNU/Linux&lt;/a&gt;是一種開源操作系統，由&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.kernel.org&#34; title=&#34;The Linux Kernel&#34;&gt;Linux&lt;/a&gt;內核和開源軟件構成。其發行版衆多，主流的有 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.redhat.com/en&#34; title=&#34;RedHat&#34;&gt;RHEL&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.centos.org&#34; title=&#34;CentOS&#34;&gt;CentOS&lt;/a&gt;、 &lt;a href=&#34;https://www.debian.org&#34; title=&#34;Debian&#34;&gt;Debian&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.ubuntu.com&#34; title=&#34;Ubuntu&#34;&gt;Ubuntu&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.suse.com&#34; title=&#34;SUSE&#34;&gt;SUSE&lt;/a&gt;/&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.opensuse.org&#34; title=&#34;OpenSUSE&#34;&gt;OpenSUSE&lt;/a&gt;。爲瞭解各發行版的產品支持週期，本人通過&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/MaxdSre/axd-ShellScript/blob/master/assets/gnulinux/gnuLinuxLifeCycleInfo.sh&#34;&gt;Shell腳本&lt;/a&gt;從各官方網站提取相關信息，並梳理成文。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>在CentOS 7中配置LEMP開發環境全記錄</title>
      <link>https://luolvshi.me/hugo2/zh/2016/lemp-stack-installation-and-configuration-on-centos-7/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 11 Mar 2016 18:31:58 +0800</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://luolvshi.me/hugo2/zh/2016/lemp-stack-installation-and-configuration-on-centos-7/</guid>
      
        <description>&lt;p&gt;本文記錄如何在已啓用&lt;code&gt;SELinux&lt;/code&gt;、&lt;code&gt;Firewalld&lt;/code&gt;防火牆的&lt;code&gt;CentOS 7&lt;/code&gt;系統中安裝、配置 &lt;strong&gt;LEMP&lt;/strong&gt; (&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nginx.com&#34; title=&#34;High Performance Load Balancer, Web Server, &amp;amp; Reverse Proxy&#34;&gt;Nginx&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mysql.com&#34; title=&#34;MySQL is the world&#39;s most popular open source database.&#34;&gt;MySQL&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://secure.php.net&#34; title=&#34;PHP is a popular general-purpose scripting language that is especially suited to web development.&#34;&gt;PHP&lt;/a&gt;)套件。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;本人寫了一些Shell腳本用以實現操作的自動化，項目代碼託管在&lt;a href=&#34;https://github.com/MaxdSre/axd-ShellScript&#34; title=&#34;axd Shell Script&#34;&gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;。已實現 系統初始化，&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.nginx.com&#34; title=&#34;High Performance Load Balancer, Web Server, &amp;amp; Reverse Proxy&#34;&gt;Nginx&lt;/a&gt;、&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.mysql.com&#34; title=&#34;MySQL is the world&#39;s most popular open source database.&#34;&gt;MySQL&lt;/a&gt;的腳本化操作，但&lt;a href=&#34;https://secure.php.net&#34; title=&#34;PHP is a popular general-purpose scripting language that is especially suited to web development.&#34;&gt;PHP&lt;/a&gt;暫時仍需要手動安裝。&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
      
    </item>
    
